data.description: **10k CREDIT AVAILABLE FOR UPGRADES OR CLOSING COSTS** In unit laundry, 1 car garage and 1 assigned parking. Welcome to this charming 2 bed, 2 bath condo nestled in a secure gated community, ideally situated just moments away from a vibrant shopping center. This inviting residence offers convenience and comfort, boasting a blend of modern amenities and thoughtful design. Step into the welcoming ambiance of this top corner unit, featuring an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The well-appointed kitchen beckons with sleek countertops and ample cabinetry. Enjoy the ease of hosting gatherings or simply relaxing in this versatile and functional layout. Unwind in the spacious primary suite, complete with an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and comfort. The second bedroom offers flexibility for guests, a home office, or a cozy retreat. Embrace the serene outdoors from your private balcony, perfect for savoring morning coffee or enjoying the evening breeze. The top-floor location ensures peace and tranquility, while the community's amenities provide relaxation and leisure. Convenience is key with the inclusion of a one-car garage and an additional carport parking space. The convenience of in-unit laundry adds to the practicality of this delightful abode. Moreover, this prime location offers easy access to the nearby freeway, simplifying commutes and enhancing accessibility to the area's array of attractions.
